 Under the same assumptions of Claims
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "lcm versus ecm"

\end_inset

 and
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
